      "content": "To convert the active heart rate from beats per second into beats per minute we must multiply 1.6 beats per second by 60 seconds.\n\n![](https://ka-perseus-images.s3.amazonaws.com/810a87bbf09a2c41bbe02b1611cd91b047f69412.png)",
